OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782038884
OL,3,CMan United legend Mark Hughes
OL,4,C'heartbroken' following sudden death
OL,5,Cof son, 38
OL,7,F"Alex was a wonderful son, brother to
OL,8,FCurtis and Xenna, devoted husband and
OL,9,Ffather to Jessica and their two
OL,10,Fbeautiful children Sebastian and
OL,11,FLeonardo. Alex was Player Recruitment
OL,12,FLead at Grimsby Town FC, and had many
OL,13,Fgood friends and colleagues. He will
OL,14,Fbe so deeply missed by us all.
OL,16,F"We ask for privacy during this sad
OL,17,Ftime as we come to terms with our
OL,18,Ffamily's loss."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
