OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782038884
OL,3,CMan United legend Mark Hughes
OL,4,C'heartbroken' following sudden death
OL,5,Cof son, 38
OL,7,FAlex Hughes had a brief playing
OL,8,Fcareer, on the books of Stockport and
OL,9,FWrexham, before joining Blackburn in
OL,10,F2007, working as a performance analyst
OL,11,Fduring his father's time as manager.
OL,13,FHe followed Mark to Manchester City in
OL,14,F2008 and worked with him again at
OL,15,FFulham before forging his own path
OL,16,Fabroad. He joined Grimsby in 2025.
OL,18,FIn a statement Grimsby Town said the
OL,19,Fclub was devastated to learn of Alex's
OL,20,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782038884
OL,3,CMan United legend Mark Hughes
OL,4,C'heartbroken' following sudden death
OL,5,Cof son, 38
OL,7,F"Alex was a devoted husband, proud
OL,8,Ffather, beloved son, brother and
OL,9,Ffriend, and a highly valued member of
OL,10,Fthe Grimsby Town family", the
OL,11,Fstatement went on.
OL,13,F"Alex joined the Mariners in 2025 and
OL,14,Fquickly became a valued and highly
OL,15,Frespected member of the football club.
OL,16,FWorking closely with Head Coach David
OL,17,FArtell and the football department, he
OL,18,Fplayed an important role in shaping
OL,19,Fthe Club's recruitment strategy and
OL,20,Fsupporting the continued development
OL,21,Fof the men's first-team squad."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782038884
OL,3,CMan United legend Mark Hughes
OL,4,C'heartbroken' following sudden death
OL,5,Cof son, 38
OL,7,FGrimsby Chairman Andrew Pettit said
OL,8,F"Everyone at Grimsby Town Football
OL,9,FClub is shocked and saddened by the
OL,10,Fnews of Alex's passing.
OL,12,F"Our deepest sympathies go out to his
OL,13,Ffamily and loved ones at this
OL,14,Fincredibly difficult time. He will
OL,15,Falways be remembered as a valued
OL,16,Fmember of the Mariners family who
OL,17,Fcontributed so much during his time
OL,18,Fwith us."
OL,26,@pD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
