PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782038884
OL,3,CMan United legend Mark Hughes
OL,4,C'heartbroken' following sudden death
OL,5,Cof son, 38
OL,7,FChief Executive Officer Polly Bancroft
OL,8,Fadded: "Alex was a much-loved and
OL,9,Fhighly respected member of the Grimsby
OL,10,FTown family.
OL,12,F"His professionalism, dedication and
OL,13,Fwarmth made a lasting impact on
OL,14,Feveryone who worked with him. I
OL,15,Fthoroughly enjoyed working alongside
OL,16,FAlex and will remember him not only as
OL,17,Fan outstanding colleague, but as a
OL,18,Fgenuinely kind person who had a
OL,19,Fpositive effect on those around him.
OL,20,FHe will be greatly missed across the
OL,21,FClub and beyond."
OL,26,@pD@HOU}D@QO]
